name: Internal-15 'Pochven' Filament
description:
The Internal-15 'Pochven' Filament permits up to 15 ships to travel from Known Space to a system in Triglavian space that is considered an internal system of the artificial constellation, or "Krai", controlled by a given Triglavian clade.

Triglavian mastery of space-time conduit technology allows them relatively fine control over the generation and targeting of FTL conduits. Certain of the filament devices used by Triglavian forces are connected to systems that are considered the "internal" systems of a Triglavian Krai, or artifical constellation controlled by a given clade. Even those unfamiliar with how to precisely target them will find the conduits they generate will transport them to an "internal system" in the Triglavian-constructed region of Pochven.
